---
title: French Onion Dip Double Chicken with Potato Wedges and Carrot Batons
description: Herbs and spices reminiscent of everyone's favourite soup - French Onion - bring elegance and oomph to your everyday chicken in the form of a savoury chicken dipper! Spiced wedges and roasted carrots are the perfect pairings of sweet and savoury.
